4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that requires no previous knowledge. The program helps students start a career as a data scientist and build their first ML models. The course duration is 16 weeks and includes 3 classes per week. The class size is limited to 12 people. Students will learn Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, and become professional Data Analysts. They will also explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, and work with supervised and unsupervised learning models. The course covers real-life cases and teaches students to tackle challenges they'll encounter in their careers. Industry-standard tools are used for strategizing and developing AI projects, from development to deployment and maintenance. The course offers certificates recognized by multiple organizations. No previous experience is required, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. For more information, visit the [4Geeks Academy website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop